{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809200/extras/GIF_Steam_00.gif?t=1725003614\" /><br>Embark on a vibrant, story-rich adventure, blending elements of classic 3D platformers and modern action-RPGs. <br><br>Journey through a broken world as Ryn, a young woman haunted by shadows of her forgotten past. Accompanied by a cat-sized dragon that grants her powerful abilities, Ryn\u2019s quest to unravel her identity is tightly intertwined with the fate of the planet. Only by mending the broken bonds of her past can she hope to restore the future. <br><br>Traverse a seamless open world of vibrant meadows, treacherous mountains, serene forests and thundering canyons. Ominous ruins and secrets are waiting to be unearthed around every corner, harboring the stories of lost civilizations, remnants of their ancient technology, and traces of your missing memories.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Exploration &amp; Upgrades:</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809200/extras/GIF_Steam_01.gif?t=1725003614\" /><br>Explore intricate environments to uncover their secrets, rewarding you with numerous ways to upgrade your skills. Appeasing playful spirits all across the world grants you access to mysterious temples, harboring even more magical abilities that will help you on your journey.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Battle &amp; Traversal:</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809200/extras/GIF_Steam_02.gif?t=1725003614\" /><br>Defeat corrupt beasts to calm their souls and restore balance. Every victory enhances your capacity to wield magic, enabling you to dash further, fly higher, and reach new areas where exciting discoveries await.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2809200/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1725003614","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steam